# Equinix SmartView MCP Server Configuration

# OAuth 2.0 Credentials (REQUIRED)
EQUINIX_CLIENT_ID=your-client-id-here
EQUINIX_CLIENT_SECRET=your-client-secret-here

# API Configuration (Optional)
EQUINIX_API_URL=https://api.equinix.com

# How to obtain credentials:
# 1. Log in to https://portal.equinix.com
# 2. Navigate to: Developer Settings > Apps
# 3. Click "Create New App"
# 4. Copy Client ID and Client Secret

# Security: Never commit .env to version control
